Definition: colorless pungent crystalline compound derived from capsicum
Example: source of the hotness of hot peppers of the genus Capsicum such as chili and cayenne and jalapeno
Synonyms: chemical_irritant, noun, plant, capsicum, s, colorless, pungent, crystalline, compound, derived, from, source, of, the, hotness, hot, peppers, genus, Capsicum, such, as, chili, and, cayenne, jalapeno
Category: noun.substance
